OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain mostly dry this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight, though it will stay rather
OL,8,Fcloudy across the south of the region.
OL,9,FIt will turn chilly under any lengthy
OL,10,Fcloud breaks, with a few fog patches
OL,11,Fpossible across Cumbria.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA bright day for many, but
OL,14,Fcloudier skies across the south will
OL,15,Fspread northwards during the
OL,16,Fafternoon, with some patchy rain
OL,17,Fdeveloping over the hills later.
OL,18,FFeeling a little milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
